books.description: Established on 28th August 2003, this library was founded by Mr. Prabhakar Vasantrao Patange with a vision to cultivate a love for reading and lifelong learning in the heart of Shree Nagar, Nanded. Since its inception, the library has served as a community hub for knowledge seekers, offering access to a diverse range of books and educational resources. Built on the values of accessibility and intellectual growth, it continues to inspire generations of readers, students, and curious minds in the region.
